fields.name: Honey
fields.description: Welsh honey, from Welsh bees. Sourced from a single hive, Melys honey is unprocessed, organic, and sourced straight from the producer. Honey, or “mel” in Welsh, is a natural sweetener and has been used for thousands of years for its anti- inflammatory and antibacterial benefits.

fields.name: Pinecone Candle
fields.description: These pine cone design candles burn clean, long and bright . They are made from beeswax and, therefore, are natural, non toxic, and produce negative ions that help purify the air.

fields.name: Love Spoon
fields.description: Lovespoons are a traditional Welsh gift, usually given to somebody you love. Handmade and carved from wood, Melys Lovespoons are the perfect decoration to show your appreciation for somebody special in your life.

fields.name: Soap
fields.description: Our honey soap is hand carved and gentle on the skin. They weigh 90g- 100g per bar, with a sweet aroma, keeping you feeling fresh for longer.

fields.name: Lip Balm
fields.description: This is an organic,  gentle and soothing product giving relief for chapped lips with no animal testing. This product is suitable for all ages.

fields.name: Bundle-Bee
fields.description: The Bundle-Bee is a limited time offer, offering both our signature honey and candle for only £12.
